message.body: Hey did you ever get my text about Stephanie? What you think of an SOA zippo lighter or blanket?
No I never got it but she has a ton of lighters and a ton of blankets though both are things she would still make use of daily. So up to you. Is it like a fleece blanket?
I think
But like.. You said it's a silly gift we get right?
Like you said she got be something silly or small right?
Yea an inexpensive gift
If you get her one of those see if Mike can get ger a knee brace. I keep forgetting to tell you guys she asked for that
But you can still get her one of those
Hmm. I'll talk to Mike
What time you think we'd do dinner Saturday
Idk like 7..8..9? Lol
I was just invited to a college graduation party Saturday....
Mike said Cassy and Jimmy invited me, him, and Eden... raincheck on that Saturday dinner?
Yea that's fine
Steph want sure if she was able to make it anyway so it might have just been me going lol
Haha. And you can't make it Friday? Cause I really want sushi lol
Well our company xmas party is Friday and idk what time we will be done. The food normally ##### so we probably won't eat there
Hey..do you have am estimate of when you think you'll be done? Like should I not hold my breath on sushi? Lol
No idea but maybe we should try for another night since we both have work early sat morning anyway
Ok that's cool
Cool... what is it? Just A painting?
Painting of Jackie
Lol I got the Jackie part.. at first I thought it was a mouse pad then I saw the brown background but yea that's really cool
